    "description": "An M5 certified-archetype health bundle carries a Stable (or LTS) public claim only when all required health indicators are green, the proof packet is current within its freshness SLO, any waiver is unexpired, and the owner is signed off. An archetype that loses any of those must drop below the cutline rather than inherit an adjacent green archetype."
